| Credential Stuffing — Successful Login After Failures — T1078
| Flags IPs that had failures then a successful login (potential compromise)

index=main sourcetype=linux_secure ("Failed password" OR "Accepted password" OR "Accepted publickey")
| rex field=_raw "from (?P<src_ip>\d+\.\d+\.\d+\.\d+)"
| eval outcome=if(match(_raw,"Failed"), "failure", "success")
| stats count(eval(outcome="failure")) as failures, count(eval(outcome="success")) as successes by src_ip
| where failures > 3 AND successes > 0
| sort -failures
